name: SYNCO Lav-S6D Dual Omnidirectional Condenser Wired Lavalier Microphone - Black
description:
Dual Lavalier Microphone
SYNCO Lav S6D adopts unique dual mic design, which can record two sound sources simultaneously in one device. You are allowed to pick up sound from two speakers and don\’t need to move the mic from one speaker to the other, which is ideal for interview, conference, Youtube podcasting, teaching, video recording, etc.
Wide Compatibility with PHONE/ CAMERA Mode
With 3.5mm TRS/TRRS connector and 6.3mm adapter, Lav S6D lapel mic can be applied to iOS/Android smartphone, DSLR, camcorder, audio recorder, mixer, laptop, PC, etc. PHONE/ CAMERA mode switch allows users to one button alter the microphone setting for different devices. No complicated adjustment is needed.
Omni-directional Condenser Capsule
Equipped with a 360 Degree omni-directional condenser capsule, SYNCO Lav-S6D boasts higher sensitivity and greater frequency response. It equally picks up sound at 360 Degree around it and faithfully reproduces the natural sound in your recording device.
Intelligent Sound Processing
CVC automatic noise reduction is a specialized technology used in SYNCO Lav-S6D lav mic. It helps to reduce the low frequency noise generated by electrical current, greatly improving the sound quality in recording. Combined with SYNCO audio decoding technology, Lav-S6D would output clear and clean voice.
19.7’ Ultra Long Cord
19.7’ (6-meter) high-quality durable cord for each side would deliver audio signals to your device steady, rapidly and truly. Your device can be set far away from the speakers and the two speakers can keep greater distances, which makes your filming more flexible without restriction.
High Quality Material
SYNCO Lav-S6D microphone provides two specialized windshields to reduce wind noise, handling noise. You can get pretty good recording result even in a noisy environment. Robust audio cable, and metal plug extend its life span for daily use.
Dual-head Sound Recording
One device with dual mic head, two users can record their sound in just one device at the same time. It is suitable for interview, conference, Youtube podcasting, teaching, video recording, etc.
Professional Sound with Specialized Tech
SYNCO Lav-S6D is an omni-directional clip-on lapel mic that employs CVC noise reduction technology and SYNCO audio decoding technology. It catches sound with more details and less low frequency noise.
Multi-device Compatibility
A 3.5mm TRS/TRRS connector and a 6.3mm adapter is for fitting SYNCO Lav-S6D dual lapel microphone in various devices, including iOS/Android smartphone, DSLR, camcorder, audio recorder, mixer, PC, laptop. One microphone, full compatibility.
PHONE/ CAMERA Mode
Two modes for accessing various devices, PHONE mode is for smartphone series, while CAMERA mode is for camera series like camera, recorder, audio mixer and laptop, one button to switch mode.
Fast Signal Transmission
19.7 feets (6-meter) anti-interference audio cord transmit voice signal to your device in high speed and high quality. It is convenient for distant shot applications.
Tips for iOS and Android Users
Some of Andorid devices may need a Type-C adapter (not included) to operate the microphone. iPhone 7 and subsequent devices require Apple\’s Lighting adapter. And the in-built photography App in Android devices is not compatible with the microphone, so you need the third-party applications to operate it.

name: SYNCO MMic-U1P Mini Cardioid Condenser Microphone for Smartphone - Black
description:
The ideal microphone for your mobile devices
If you like to record with your smartphone or tablet and the sound quality offered by similar equipment is not good enough for you, the compact Synco U1 microphone will be the perfect choice! This lightweight and compact, cardioid device optimises audio in real time to give you the best possible results. With a 90° swivel range, you can easily adapt it to the situation and record everything exactly as you want it to.
Record with your smartphone and enjoy perfect sound quality
The device is characterised by its Instant Signal Processing Circuit, which makes it possible to improve the audio quality of your phone or tablet when the audio wave is received in real time. That is not all! Thanks to the cardioid condenser, the microphone focuses the sound exactly where you point it and reduces unnecessary ambient noise. With the Synco U1, you will see that mobile devices can also provide crystal clear sound
Adjust its position to your current situation
You can freely rotate the U1 by up to 90°, allowing you to point it where you want to go. Set it to the direction you want the camera to record and enjoy the best possible results. You can also adjust its position to suit the situation as you go along. Record yourself or your friends and enjoy the exceptional flexibility of this remarkable microphone!
The perfect tool for recording with mobile devices
Synco U1 is ideal for people recording with mobile devices such as smartphones or tablets. Using this practical microphone, you don\’t have to worry about cables, batteries or adapters. Simply connect it directly to your equipment and start recording! The devices are compatible with USB C, iPhone Lightning or 3.5mm TRRS ports.

You can always have it with you
The length of the device is similar to the length of your finger and its weight does not exceed 20g. This allows you to successfully connect the Synco U1 to your phone – the microphone will neither load it nor cover the screen or camera lenses. You can also have this compact device always at hand – in your bag, backpack or even in your pocket. What\’s more, despite its inconspicuous design, the device is extremely durable – its metal parts make it resistant to changing weather conditions and make it easy to use, e.g. when recording in the mountains or on a bicycle.

name: SYNCO CMic-V1 Desktop USB Large Diaphragm Condenser Professional Microphone - Black
description:
CMic V1 is the first USB powered large diaphragm condenser microphone of SYNCO. It features studio grade specifications providing extended dynamic range, warm and clear sound, and strong SPL capability, and includes everything for live streaming, as well as for perfect recording in outdoor speech and home studio where sound detail capture is a necessity.
Large Diaphragm for Accurate Pickup
SYNCO V1, a professional condenser microphone, carries a large diaphragm condenser capsule to precisely convert sound waves into mic signals, accurately pick up sound and deliver highly restored sound. The gold plated PTFE diaphragm is highly sensitive, allowing the mic to reproduce subtle sounds.
Studio grade Params for Master-quality Sound
The 20Hz—20KHz frequency response offers flexibility to accurately reproduce signals from varied sources, and the 16bit/ 48KHz sampling rate brought by inbuilt DSP chip makes nice flat response to voice. They work with the anti-interference metal construction to provide higher-than-CD sound.
Sound Focused for Neutral Pick up
The cardioid polar pattern reduces pickup of sounds from sides and rear and improves isolation of desired sound source. With high SPL capturing loud signals with minimal noise and distortion and excellent transient response allowing this electret condenser microphone to follow sound waves more accurately, it gives an original and detailed sound image.
USB-powered Operation for Simple Recording
The USB/ OTG cable provides the USB condenser microphone V1 with a direct, convenient connection to computer, phone or tablet. It ensures a stable 5V power supply and a secure and excellent signal transfer without any drivers. It’s never been easier to get quality sound from singing, gaming, chatting, etc.
User-friendly Design for Easy Use
A 3.5mm headphone output allows real-time audio monitoring; the gain control and mute buttons support easier and quicker adjustment; the desktop holder provides convenience for dubbing, live streaming, etc.

name: SYNCO WMic-T1 Camera-Mount 16-Channel UHF Wireless Lavalier Microphone System - Black
description:
The Synco WMic T1 is a camera mount wireless lavalier microphone system offering a simple and complete solution for videographers, vloggers, and mobile journalists who need to record quality speech to cameras, camcorders, or mobile devices such as smartphones and tablets.
The WMic T1 includes an omnidirectional lavalier microphone for convenient voice capture in video shoots, interviews, and more, and its locking 3.5mm TRS mini plug prevents accidental disconnection from the bodypack transmitter. The receiver can be hooked on your belt, attached to a camera shoe, or mounted on a tripod. Connect its 3.5mm output to the mic input of your camera with the supplied TRS cable or to the input of your mobile device with the included TRRS cable.
The receiver and transmitter feature 16 switchable channels to help you avoid interference, adjustable volume for easy management of audio levels, and up to 10 hours of run time via AA batteries (available separately).

Complete Wireless Solution

Compact receiver with belt clip and shoe/tripod mount
Bodypack transmitter with belt clip
Omnidirectional lavalier microphone with locking 3.5mm TRS mini plug

16 switchable channels for recording without environmental interference
Adjustable volume on receiver and transmitter
Up to 10 hours of run time via AA batteries (available separately)

Easy Connectivity

name: SYNCO WMic-TS Dual Camera-Mount UHF Wireless Omni Lavalier Microphone System - Black
description:
The Synco WMic TS is a clear sounding, easy to-use wireless lavalier microphone system with two microphones and just one receiver. It provides vloggers, mobile journalists, Youtubers, and videographers with a complete solution for recording dialogue, interviews, and speech with two persons talking simultaneously—directly to a mirrorless/DSLR camera or a smartphone equipped with a headphone jack.
The lightweight WMic-TS consists of two compact transmitters each with its own built-in microphone and a separate omnidirectional lavalier microphone. When using the lavalier mics, the transmitters can be clipped on your belt. When using the built-in microphones, the transmitters can be positioned on a table for sit-down interviews or held in hand and operated as handheld microphones.
Also compact, the receiver mounts on your camera shoe. It plugs into your camera or mobile device using the included 3.5mm TRS or TRRS cables. A headphone jack allows you to monitor the audio from both transmitters in real time to ensure that you are capturing a clean signal. The 15-level gain control lets you to adjust your recording level to accommodate audio ranging from quiet speaking to booming sounds.
The system provides up to 8.5 hours of continuous use on USB-rechargeable batteries at a range up to 492\’. You can choose from 60 frequencies to find a clean channel and avoid interference, and up to 12 WMic-TS can be deployed simultaneously in the same location if more audio channels are needed.
Save Space on Your Shooting Rig
The two-channel receiver allows you to save space on your shooting rig by using a single receiver to simultaneously accept signals from two transmitters/microphones.
Built-In Mic for True Wireless
The transmitter is equipped with a built-in microphone and a 3.5mm mic input that accepts the included lavalier microphone.
For a truly wireless experience, the transmitter can be clipped on clothing without having to wire yourself or your talent.
Lavalier Mic Included
For a more discreet setup, use the small lavalier microphone, which can be easily concealed away from the camera\’s eye.
Bright OLED Displays
The large OLED displays make it easy to see vital information, such as battery status, audio level, and group/channel selection—even in bright sunlight.
Mono and Stereo Recording
You have the option to switch between a mono or a stereo output on the receiver. Recording in mono combines both microphones on both the left and right side of your audio track. Recording in stereo puts one person on the left and the other person on the right, allowing you to isolate each person\’s dialog and adjust each level individually later in post.
Clear and Reliable Synco Wireless Technology
Synco wireless LinkLable technology analyzes and calculates the frequency data using built-in smart chips to deliver a clear transmission at up to 492\’ (line-of-sight) or 262\’ (with obstruction).
The transmitters are equipped with a selectable high and low RF transmission setting, so you can use a more powerful setting for longer distances, or a lower setting for shorter distances and longer run time.
At a Glance

Low-cut filter helps reduce unwanted wind and traffic noises.
180° foldable antennas make it easy for users to carry the system around.
Headphone jack for monitoring in real time.
15 levels of gain control.
The transmitters and the receiver are powered via a built-in lithium-ion rechargeable battery.
8.5 hours of operating time on a full charge.
Includes 3-in-1 USB charging cable.

name: SYNCO WAir-G1 (A2) Dual 2.4GHz UltraCompact Digital Wireless Microphone System - Black
description:
The Synco WAir G1 A2 is an ultracompact, digital wireless microphone system with two microphones and just one receiver—great for shooting two person videos for Instagram, YouTube, and TikTok. It offers a complete, versatile, and simple-to-use solution for recording dialogue, interviews, and speech directly to a mirrorless/DSLR camera or a mobile device with a 3.5mm input.
The WAir-G1-A2 consists of two tiny, lightweight clip-on transmitters each with its own built-in microphone along with a separate lavalier mic that can be used if you prefer a more discreet mic setup. The system also includes a single tiny receiver that mounts on your camera or mobile device and plugs into its 3.5mm input jack. Both a 3.5mm TRS cable for camera use and a 3.5mm TRRS cable for smartphone use are included.
The system delivers reliable transmission with clear sound at a line-of-sight distance up to 164\’ (98\’ with limited obstacles). The built-in rechargeable batteries provide up to 5 hours of operation and recharge in 1.5 hours via USB Type-C ports.
Two Microphones into One Receiver

The two-channel receiver allows you to save space on your shooting rig by using a single receiver to simultaneously receive signals from the two mic/transmitters.
The receiver features a belt clip, which also doubles as a shoemount adapter for your camera.
Clip-On Transmitters with Built-In Mics and Lavalier Mics

Each of the compact transmitters is equipped with both a built-in microphone and a 3.5mm input that accepts its included lavalier microphone.
The transmitter can be clipped on clothing without having to wire yourself or your talent, providing a fast, truly wireless setup. You can also hold the transmitter in your hand and use it as a handheld microphone.
A low-cut filter on the transmitter can be engaged to reduce air-conditioning and wind noise.
Easy-to-Operate System

Simply press the pairing buttons and the system components pair automatically.
Dedicated gain buttons on the receiver allow for 10 dB of gain adjustment for each microphone independently.
The receiver and the transmitters have displays that indicate power, battery life, and pairing status.
You have the option to switch between mono or stereo on the receiver: Recording in mono combines both microphones on both the left and right side of your audio track. Recording in stereo puts one person on the left and the other person on the right, allowing you to isolate each person\’s dialog and adjust each level individually later in post.
The transmitters and the receiver are powered for up to 5 hours via a built-in lithium-ion rechargeable battery.
The battery recharges in 1.5 hours; a charging cable is included.
Monitor in Real Time

If your camera doesn’t have a headphone jack, you can monitor your sound via the receiver’s 3.5mm headphone output while recording to ensure that you are capturing a clean signal.
2.4 GHz Digital Wireless

To avoid interference from TV and radio waves, the WAir digital system operates in the 2.4 GHz frequency band—far away from television, radio, and UHF wireless microphone transmissions.
The system automatically changes transmission frequency to mitigate noise and dropouts at a line-of-sight distance of up to 164 feet or up to 98 feet when some obstacles are present.
For optimal performance, environments with limited Wi-Fi/2.4 GHz traffic and minimal physical obstructions are recommended.

name: SYNCO Vlogger Kit1 with Microphone & Fill Light for Camera/SmartPhone - Black
description:
Designed for mobile video creators, the Vlogger Kit 1 from SYNCO combines necessary items to help users produce videos for social media. Included in this kit is a Mic M1S Shotgun Mic, an LED video light, a Smartphone Video Rig, a 360° Mini Tripod, a 3.5mm Phone Cable, and a Shock Mount.
The shotgun mic features a cardioid pickup pattern to help reduce ambient noise, plus improved shock absorption to help reduce vibrations, while the LED light uses 48 individual LEDs to provide illumination, with brightness levels that can be adjusted from 0 to 100% and a color temperature that is adjustable from 2700 to 6500K and can last for up to 90 minutes at full brightness. The included smartphone video rig helps stabilize handheld or stationary use and can accommodate accessories such as a mic, fill light, or tripod via the cold shoe and 1/4\” 20 threads. To better realize various filming angles, a mini tripod has a ball head that may be adjusted 360°. Also included is a shock mount and a 3.5mm phone cable.
General Features
All in-One Vloggin Kit
What most mobile video creators desire is premium content with the simplest equipment. The SYNCO Vlogger Kit combines all necessary things you require in a kit to help you produce amazing videos.
Improved Sound Quality
With a larger condenser (Φ14) to catch more detailed audio signals, the SYNCO Mic-M1S shotgun microphone outputs natural sound with less self-generated noise. A cardioid polar pattern helps reduce ambient noise.
Natural Fill Light
The LED video light offers typical lighting modes for better visual effect. In CCT Mode, color temperature (2700 to 6500K) and brightness (0 to 100%) are at your command. EFF Mode is for special lighting, lightning and fire. Weighing 3.88 oz, it also includes a parameter display screen in its compact size. It faithfully restores object color with 95+ high color rendering index, making you shine in live streaming.
Easy Installation
The SYNCO Vlogger Kit provides a smartphone video rig for handheld or stationary use. Made of ABS plastic, it is light for carrying around. You could attach microphone, fill light, tripod and other devices to it via the cold shoe mounts and 1/4\” threads. Get everything tidy. The mini tripod features a 360° swivel ball head for various filming angles.

name: SYNCO MC4 4-Channel Professional Audio Mixer with USB Audio Interface - Black
description:
Allow You More Detailed Adjustment
Professionalize your sound with SYNCO MC4 mixing console. The gain of input signal, treble and bass tone, volume are flexibly controllable. The EFX button offers reverb effect. Each of the channels could be regulated separately for the above functions. In live streaming, you can connect microphone and musical instrument synchronously and make separate refined modulation for instant output. SYNCO MC4 mixer can be used with mobile phone and computer through Bluetooth or USB connection. With a headphone jack, you can monitor the audio production in real time.
Broadcast Quality Audio processing
The high precision preamplifier in SYNCO MC4 audio mixer improves the signal to noise ratio and captures the slightest difference in vocal or instrument performance, recording the original sound for you when live streaming. Featuring 24 bit/192KHz high resolution, it efficiently handles the signals in high fidelity and delivers ideal sound for broadcasting even after processing. No audio distortion in your live channel!
All in-one for Easy Operation
SYNCO MC4 integrates analog mixer, power amplifier and effect processor into a compact, portable unit. It provides 4 channels tuning, including two mono input channels, one stereo input channel and a USB input channel, suitable for recording studio, public address system, music bar, broadcasting, live streaming, television, and film post-production.
Versatile Connectivity for Multiple Devices
One mixer adapts to varied devices. A 3.5 mm TRS to 2-Male RCA Adapter Cable and a 3.5 mm TRRS to Dual 3.5 mm TRSF Y Cable are attached to the product package for easy connection. Equipped with 6.3mm, 3.5mm, XLR, RCA inputs and USB interface, the mixer applies to various equipment, such as condenser microphone, dynamic mic, wireless microphone, guitar, passive speaker, MP3, and PC.
Micro USB Charging/48V Phantom Power
Designed with a micro USB port, SYNCO MC4 mixer can be powered by computer, power adapter and power bank, while providing 48V phantom power for microphones with XLR plug. name: RAY Sanitizer Spray (Pen) 10ml
description:
RAY Sanitizer Blue
Net Weight: 10 ml b

DGDA (Drug Administration) Approved WHO Recommended Formula
Kills 99.9% of germs

Contains 75% Isopropyl Alcohol BP
Active Instantly without Water
Soothing Fresh Fragrance
Pump-action Dispenser
Non-irritating
Enriched with Moisturizer, Skin Softening Formula

Directions: Spray max 3 puffs on the palm and rub on both sides of the two hands and fingertips together until dry.
Use: After contact with surfaces in public places, Before cooking/eating and touching infants, After eating, using the toilet and attending an ill person, Before and after changing baby’s diaper and contacting with pets, During Travel.
Caution: Keep away from fire/flame and children’s reach. Avoid contact with eyes, nose, mouth and broken skin. In case of eye contact, rinse eyes thoroughly with water. If swallowed, contact a doctor!
